text:
Gangwar, Bakait sir ya fir Gawd. inme se kisi bhi naam se inhe refer kr skte hain. Baatein start hui jab tum room me aate the aur soumya aur tum pata nhi kya kya high level baatein krte the. Samajh me mere aata tha nhi. Pehle lagta tha ki yaar bichaare ki tayaari nhi ho paayi hgai isiliye itna pareshaan hai. Toh jo bhi yeh memoir padh raha ho toh jaan lein ki inse baat krke lagega aapko ki aapki kaafi achhi tayaari ho chuki hai. Naa hin inhe aap kabhi kaafi zyada effort lagate paayenge. Pr jab aap marks dekhoge toh lagega ki yeh us ek marks katne ke liye ro rha tha? 
Jokes apart, he is an overacheiver, jo kabhi bhi exam ka aapko help krne ke liye ready rahega. The cool, chill baikait with big smile on his face. All the best bro. 

Haan yeh bro bohot bolta hai. Zomato me milte hin rehna hai ab toh Bro.
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)

text: Aur Mota Bhai kaise ho 2nd year mein "Are yaar kya karun bahut time waste ho raha hai yahan" poochhne se coding mein kaafi aaga, machine learning mei kaafi aage, software development mei kaafi aage, stock market mei kaafi aage aur TT Mein toh pahle bhi the. Yaar tumne huamre 3rd year ka kahane ka poora mast menu krwaa diya tha. Sab log milkr fir bhi kaafi praeshaan krte the tumhe pr kabhi hote hin nhi the pareshaan tum. Sahi mein waise bataun toh baten kaafi hui hai tumse pr main mai tumhe abhi jab college khula tha tabhi deeply jaana. Kaafi mast ho yaar tum to. Yaar mera paer theek karvane ke liye thanks. The guy with a warm smile, kaafi mast smile hai. joki kabhi bura nhi maanta aur apna hin mazaak khud uda kr doosron ko hasata hai. Little bit introvert and always stands by his ethics. Haan bus khaane me inka koi ethics nhi hai. Jo bhi khaana jo sab khatam kr dega yeh banda. A very down to earth guy jo humesha help krne ke liye ready hai except exam me. Aisa vyakti jo kaafi youtube me aane ka prayaas krta hai. jisne hume fifa khilwaya. Yaar mujhe toh waise kaafi cheezon ke liye thanks kehna hai pr aaram se kahenge. HumareBus keep the smile on aur aise hin mehnat krte raho aur inspire bhi. Aur mote naha liya kr. Mai toh jab aaya tha tb hin naha liya tha mat bolna itne proudly  :P . Thanks yaar for coming to our wing. Agli baar TT me hara dungfa mai tujhe.
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)

text: Yo Animeda!!! Behen toh banaya nhi tune mujhe. Physics toh chill hai Ho hin jaayegaa. Aur usi ke saath mera physics mein itna Jyada marks dilva aane ke liye thanks. tab main samajh gaya ki is bacche se padhaai ka advice nahi lena hai. physics ke bare mein pura deep mein padh leta hai pr syllabus ka Nahi padega. Tere saath sath mein batein karna aur teri ajeebo garreb kahaniyaan sunna, Patte khelna, Phatte khelna, basketball khelna sab cheez, Kaafi Maze dilwaaye tune. Apne Naam per pura Khada Utra hai tu, aur pure Ctop ko anime Dikhane mein, Main Tera Hi Hath hai. thanks sath mein Baitha kar, anime dikhwaane ke liye aur games khilane ke liye. sabse jyada to thanks humesha saath hone ke liye. kisi bhi situation me tere jaisa cool rehna seekhna hai yaar. Haan tere jaisa pr gussa krna toh bilkul nhi seekhna hai. Chal gurgaon aata hoon toh milte hain. Yaar waise koi anime bata na please.
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)

text: Kiran Bero!!!!!! Tum aur soumya yeh do log ho jo shi mei apne jese lagte ho ❤️❤️(plagiarism detected). Yaar bus jo code bheja hai usme variable change toh kr lena kamse kam. Thanks humesha madad krne ke liye. Yaar kya hin kahun. Shaadi me toh bulaaunga hin pr usse pehle hum teen kahan jaayenge?? Sponsor kr dena yaar. Saath me batti club, saath me pubg, are waise saath me bsbe ke room se khana khana, waise vo toh tum akele bhi kr hin lete the, saath har cheez hum teeno ka.  Yeh pakke se best trio hai. Yaar plan banate hain. Haan memoir me naa bhi likhun tb bhi jo bhabhi hain meri jab padh rhi hongi toh hum unhe kahaniyaan toh bata hin rhe honge. Waise vo screen shot abhi bhi hai mere paas. Yaar yeh soumya daga de raha hai. Dhokhe baaz insaan. Isike wajah se hum teen kr nhi paa rhe kaam. Jldi se plan banate hain aur kahin milte hain wapas se aur maze krnegee kaafi. Best of luck yaar.
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)

text:
Varshney bhaiii. Yaar mast roomie the tum. Ek bhi trareef krne ka mann nhi kr raha mera yahan.  Aadat hin nhi hai. Ek toh papa mummy yahan dimaag kharaab kiye rakhe hain ki dekho mature bachhe ko. Bhppp. dono ke dono sote aur pade rehte the bed pr. Ek yogi tha jo jag jaata tha pr use bhi aadat lagwaa di thi. Freinds lover aur haan jo ise pasand hai vo tumhe dikhwaa kr maanega yeh. Pr ultimately vo content hote great hain. Except kuch jo shayad JAiDEEP samjh raha hoga. Yaar ek toh itna hifi english mat likha kro. Aadha memoir samjh nhi aaya mujhe apna. 
Kaafi janawar ladka jise galti se achhi shakal mil gyi hai aur achha style mil gya hai. Galti se cool dikhne wala ladka. The least dedicated guy joki raat bhar jag kr agar complete nhi hua hai toh khud bhi padega aur baaki ko bhi batayega. Prateek 15 min me utha dena jab bhi mai kehta tha toh ok bol kr yeh bhi so jaata tha aur jab bhi yeh mujhe kehta tha toh mai bhi soo jaata tha. Are yaar kyun likh raha hoon pehle yeh batao yahan. Humesha toh milte rahenge hin. Tbhi nhi milenge jab tum bhagwaan ke payaare ho jaaoge. 
Har list me top krne wala banda hai yeh. Humare C top ki bhi list bani thi usme bhi top kiya tha. Aur welcome maine tumhari saari convex ki aur advanced ml ka kaam kr diya tha. Waise jo bhi padh rha ho memoir unhe agar Formal letters se lekr sops ya fir kuch bhi technology ke baare me updates chahiye isse le skte ho. Thank me later! 
C-Top's fakir aadmi joki jhola utha kr raat ke 2 bjue bhi chal lenge RM or KD. The guy having 48 hrs in one day --->chalo mail aa gya 
20th tk ho gyi date. 
yahan se baad me continue krenge
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)

text: Eklaute aise mitra mere college ke jise kisi aur se zyada dosti krte dekhkr jalan hone lagti thi mujhe. Sabse zyada innocent aur starting me toh bilkul bhi oppose nhi krne wala but isiliye taaki saamne wale ko bura na lage. Sabka kaam apne sir pr lene ko duty maanane wala aur har cheez ki councelling krne wala. Pata nhi mai kaise tumhe sahi lag gya pr thanks roomie banane ke liye. Summers me project krna, jiske sapne me pubg aa jaata tha, seeti bajana aur seekhna, swimming, bady, football, basketball, cricket aur har ek gaane ka lyrics yaad rakhna, snt me jeetna chahe apna project ho ya fir inter iit me doosron ka project ho. Yahan tk elections me jitwana. Kya kya nhi kiya tumne?? Mai batata hoon waise ki catch haanth failaa kr bhaagte hue krne ka try kya mast tha.   . Haan tum jab bhi party me bulaane ke liye yeh kehte the ki tum nhi jaaoge toh mai bhi nhi jaaunga uspr mana kr paana bohot mushkil ho jaata tha pr vo kaafi achha lagta tha mujhe, thanks. Are yaar tareef krne me ajeeb lag raha hai, aage firse nhi krunga  kabhi Miss Soumyaaa. Pata nhi chala ek toh ladki ka naam hai ya ladke ka. Saath me har kaam krne ke liye bohot achha companion choose kiya tha tumne. Welcome welcome. Haan last day likh raha hoon pr   sabse pehle tumhara hin likh raha hoon. All the best jo kr rhe ho uske liye. Ab maine wish kr diya toh pakka ho hin jaana hai. Welcome welcome. Thanks padha dene ke liye aur naiyaa paar lagwaa dene ke liye. Youtube pr gaana loop me laga kr jab tum gaana gaate the tbhi maine tumhe apne band ke liye as a singer recruit kr liya tha. Jldi thoda ab time mile bus aur wapas se maze kr paayein jo krte the. Aapas me humesha ek doosre ko chidhana bus baakiyon ke saamne milkr unko chidhane me kaafi maza aata tha. Thanks for being my bestestest Male (vo samjh rhe ho naa) friend. Tumhari galat sangat ke wajah se hin maine BBQ me mocktail piya tha aur uske baad room pr aakr (aage continue krna hai kya)?? Apni first conversation hui thi bhoot ki baaton se pr tumhare aawaz joki tum ishq mubaarak gaa rhe the usne mera dhayan aakarshit kiya tha. Jldi se corona khatam ho aur milein toh isi gaane pr ab casio bajayenge (Zara zara toh bhoto baja liye kyun). Chalo padhne jaao ab, kaafi time chala gya tumhara. Waise thanks again, college ke almost har achhe memories me tum rhe ho. is baar bus college aa jaate toh shayad mai utna bore nhi hota. Maze kaafi kiye but jo maze krne ka average level set ho chuka tha tumhare saath usse kam hin reh paaya.
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)

Uncle ko vo wale messages ka kahani batane wale aur na jaane kitno ke dil todne wala ladka. Saathe me dhoni ko jitwaane ka kitna try nhi kiya humne. Humare hin superstitions ke wajah se hin waise jeeta hai vo. “But they never did, ever lived, ebbing and flowing Inhibited, limited” se lekr “are you ready?? Dhu dhu dhu dhu dhu.. Surwaan bhi 16va vi tappeya 17va vi tappeya (what!) 18ve ‘ch munda badnam ho gaya” gaana gaane tak ka safar kaafi achha raha. 
Yaar us mote animeda ne jo anime hunter x hunter dikhaya tha toh kya new year manaye the hum log. Shrotriya ek shift krta tha aur fir hum dono doosre shift me. Aur yaar thanks jo daant daant kr aur taana maar maar kr mujhe class le jaate the. Ek time hota tha jab sab humare room me ikattha hote the fir vo kuch hua pata nhi shayad bed alag alag kr diye the galti se shayad. Tbhi se pata nhi kyun kam krte gye. Yaar aur darwaaza band krke padhne time ek toh aawaz bhi nhi aa paati thi knock ki. Chill hai vo toh. 
Achhe achhe idea dene ke liye thanks ki kaise chupaaun aur kya krun my better half se baat krne ke liye. Pata nhi papa mummy ko itne bhole kyun lagte ho tum ki dekho Shivam ek soumya bhi hai aur ek tum ho. Unhe kya pata ki yhi hai jise sab pata hai. 
Waise summers me mai maan chuka tha ki tum roomie toh noi hin banoge toh mai poochna hin nhi chah raha tha. Lagta tha karan aur tum hin banoge. Pr fir ban gye hum dono roomie mast tumne pooch liya tha.  
Vo raat ke 4 bje tk badi khelne me bhi kaafi maza aata tha yaar. Fir beech me jab Counter strike ka chaska laga tha. Kaafi kam time ke liye pr maza kaafi aaya tha. Salman khan ke maha bhakt ho tum. Uske jaisa bracelet pehenne tk toh theek tha. Pr tumne toh uske birthday ke din hin apna rakh liya. Aisa kyun?? 
Are waise mujhe kya topi pehnaya tha tumne standup time mere jokes ki tareef kr krke, jab mai room me practice kr raha tha. Fir wapas jab apne us video ko dekhta hoon tb lagta hai kya hin dooston ke kehne pr aakr kiya. 
Waise us din jab basket ball ground pr hum log baat kr rhe the, toh kaash jo un pujari uncle ne bataya hoga tumhe, vo galat nikla ho. Are waise itne mehnat se padha tha tumne pschyology pr afsos wapas se tumhare lottery me vhi mila tumko(ek lauta course jo hum wingies se zyada tumhara saath nhi choodna chahta tha). Darawne movie ka crazy, jaise a quite place dhekte time mai sahi me darr kr chilla deta tha toh yeh daant deta tha ki mai jaanboojh ke kr raha hoon. Thanks tumne lone ranger dekh liya ultimately. Nhi toh use dekhte time 500 baar toh soo chuke ho tum. Lights off krke mahaul jama kr movie laga kr khud soo jata tha.
HAr cheez hum dono kaafi enthu se start krte the phir lastly tum mera bojh bhi utha kr khud complete krte the. Hackathons dena microsoft, flipkart ka ya fir raat bhar rust ka, ya fir reinforcement learning ke liye vo car khareedne ke planning krna. Robots aur insaan pr discuss krna aur poore time bulla kaatna saath me. 
Tumhari galat sangat ke wajah se hin maine BBQ me mocktail piya tha aur uske baad room pr aakr (aage continue krna hai kya)?? Apni first conversation hui thi bhoot ki baaton se pr tumhare aawaz joki tum ishq mubaarak gaa rhe the usne mera dhayan aakarshit kiya tha. text: Aur UGP wale teacher ne kitne classes lin abhi tk?? Saara anime aur series dekh kr padh bhi liya kar  kabhi kabhaar. Tere jokes se zyada Tere Hasi per Hasi Aati hai. Aur vo snowman wala joke sunana. Simple, down to earth, humesha help krne ke liye ready aur sabse zyada innovative aur asli engineer. dekh le tu kitna bhi taakatvar ho pr mere se panje Mein Har jaata hai yeh baat yaad rakhiyo. are Yaar Tera Jo Ghar Se Tu Jab aata tha to ho jo tu khana lata tha vo bahut miss krunga. Bhola Sa baccha Shrotriya Se Jyada baccha to tu hai waise. baten to hoti Rahegi. Dhyan Rakhna apna. And beaware of yogi. haan jo bhi iska memoir padh raha ho, unhe agar kuch bhi kaam krwana ho toh ise bus paneer ka ghoos de dijiye aur vo kaam done. Kuch bhi kaam.
author: Shivam Kumar (B Kumar)
